CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 17, 1956, pg. B12, reads: "Harvest Bazaar at Madison - A harvest bazaar was held by the Madison P-TA at the school. Shown here are members of the committee which made the annual affair a great success.  From left: Mrs. Jacob Williams, Mrs. Christine Mueller, teacher-advisor; Mrs. William Lovett [Lovette], president of the P-TA; Mrs. Frances McNairy and Mrs. Houston Parks. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Betty Jean Williams, Christine Mueller, Thelma Lovette, Frances McNairy, and Mrs. Houston Parks gathered around "General Store" display at Harvest Bazaar, Madison Elementary School, another version
